{"tid":1295735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同大家講少少野，我地依家做緊嘅事係犯法，但我地係為公義而犯法","createTime":"2019-07-08T06:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:28:40.000Z","uid":232817,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8cc392e16d27212819f76f223bc8ff9ccdaa1a","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:19:53.000Z","msg":"我打依篇文嘅原因，係因為經過尋晚旺角一役後，開始睇到唔少言論係覺得示威者真係&quot;無辜&quot;，&quot;冇犯法&quot;，所以希望藉住依篇文令大家重新認識返自己做緊乜。<br />\n今次我想集中講下&quot;佔領&quot;行為。<br />\n我明白依家佔領好似變左最低消費，大大小小嘅示威都會出現唔同規模嘅佔領，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但我想大家認清一點，佔領馬路本身絕對係一個違法行為。</span><br />\n我唔係想怪責任何示威者，而係我希望大家搞清楚一件事，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地依家係透過違法行為，對社會造成一定程度嘅衝擊，從而施壓於政府去回應我地嘅訴求，</span><br />\n即使我地做嘅事係正義，但仍然係犯法，只係我地願意冒著即使要承擔法律責任嘅險都選擇以依種方式抗爭，<br />\n最好嘅例子係7.1衝擊立法會，死士喺清楚明白有機會被控暴動嘅情況下選擇以衝擊立法會去表達訴求，<br />\n大家記住我地唔係出黎玩，而係做嘅每件事都有風險。<br />\n<br />\n點解我會講依啲，係因為我見到好多人話尋晚警察唔應該拉人，講到示威者好慘，<br />\n但我想問下，乜佢地唔係已經清楚晒風險先佔馬路咩？點解依家講到警察拉人係錯？<br />\n我覺得大家需要搞清楚一件事...<br />\n非法霸佔馬路係一件違法嘅事，我地要屌嘅係屌佢暴力清場(不恰當武力)，而唔係屌佢話你犯法...<br />\n我希望大家以後做任何事真係清楚個風險再做，如果唔係終有一日會玩出火"},{"pid":"c421df350883c166663022af566502b9c8c8a639","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:21:50.000Z","msg":"利申返：我唔係幫警察講任何好話，我個人絕對仇警，但仇警係一回事，唔會因為警察仆街而令我地做嘅犯法行為變成合法"},{"pid":"731d7fb59b91e322e7c073961d1a7b240b406f1d","tid":1295735,"uid":52200,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:22:22.000Z","msg":"場仗未打完架！五大訴求未接納，一眾被捕士未釋放，林鄭未鞠躬，盧偉聰未落台，外國戰線啱啱先開始(在此向攬炒巴致敬)，現階邊個同政府對話邊個就係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEbbGfV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEbbGfV.jpg&h=252d433f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMfoug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMfoug.jpg&h=5527c394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qANusVW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqANusVW.jpg&h=5737c822&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6QQzD2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6QQzD2C.jpg&h=5961c3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0zD2D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0zD2D.jpg&h=747e3cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL0LLHD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL0LLHD.jpg&h=496d3a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZythBPj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZythBPj.jpg&h=f98e34dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"390ab11d7f72e6948fd7a2f66194c61bd8715903","tid":1295735,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個英雄四起,百花齊放既時代<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dfrqFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dfrqFS</a>"},{"pid":"8a1c798736def240481936d305a816342a0e7b6c","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"推，有唔同意嘅歡迎提出"},{"pid":"75644e682649fa52a9bba07f5f36c6241aa95438","tid":1295735,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"犯法但無罪"},{"pid":"4e18e21da5f33169c9f1af9adaa4db890400dc85","tid":1295735,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"藍絲只會話 搵個公園靜靜地示威咪唔犯法 唔好影響到人 人地鋪租幾貴呀一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔識駁"},{"pid":"d03f59adfc7a6c4f172f68ef415bd7730c28d7b9","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75644e682649fa52a9bba07f5f36c6241aa95438","tid":1295735,"uid":114121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"犯法但無罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:26:53.000Z","msg":"有冇罪係等法官判（實際上），或者由社會去評論（意義上），<br />\n但仍然係犯法，兩者必須要分清楚！"},{"pid":"dc5207886f727dbe5b637225cd1904b5fd9c2266","tid":1295735,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"捉到咪犯法 捉唔到咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11a4bc50e843913bd1c95dc397042de9791a773a","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4e18e21da5f33169c9f1af9adaa4db890400dc85","tid":1295735,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"藍絲只會話 搵個公園靜靜地示威咪唔犯法 唔好影響到人 人地鋪租幾貴呀一日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔識駁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:28:13.000Z","msg":"&quot;我地依家係透過違法行為，對社會造成一定程度嘅衝擊，從而施壓於政府去回應我地嘅訴求&quot;"},{"pid":"3284ecac00135b480a371493218cc8270daed57f","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc5207886f727dbe5b637225cd1904b5fd9c2266","tid":1295735,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:27:43.000Z","msg":"捉到咪犯法 捉唔到咪冇事囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:28:51.000Z","msg":"冇錯，但我睇到個情況係，<br />\n好多人出過好多次都冇比人捉到，就以為自己真係冇犯法"},{"pid":"4196407b626eb83362f0e5964f02fe6b90dd9a56","tid":1295735,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22f1fa6d49208a1a24ed44eab7bff567a819ce04","tid":1295735,"uid":7832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:31:20.000Z","msg":"犯法唔係犯罪<br />\n更何況條法律根本不能制衡有權力既機關"},{"pid":"309ec90b653235b03e04d68daa6db3a3ccf83580","tid":1295735,"uid":260806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:35:38.000Z","msg":"根據中國共產黨自己嘅理論<br />\n法律、監獄、警察、法庭只係爲<ins>統治階級</ins>服務嘅